---
const pageTitle = "Workforce Intelligence | Luanda Rodrigues";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Painel interativo de workforce combinando risco de turnover, pressão de mercado e métricas prontas para BI."
  />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="/workforce-intelligence" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/assets/logo/monogram.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#050505;--ink:#f7f3ea;--soft:#cdc7ba;--muted:#837e74;--line:rgba(247,243,234,.12);--line-strong:rgba(247,243,234,.18);--panel:rgba(255,255,255,.035);--panel-strong:rgba(255,255,255,.06);--panel-deep:rgba(255,255,255,.018);--acid:#d7ff6f;--blue:#98c1ff;--teal:#5ac8d8;--amber:#f0b35f;--red:#ff7676;--heading:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif}
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{background:var(--bg);scroll-behavior:smooth;color-scheme:dark}
    body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden}
    body:before{content:"";position:fixed;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 78% 2%,rgba(215,255,111,.10),transparent 22%),radial-gradient(circle at 8% 24%,rgba(152,193,255,.08),transparent 26%),linear-gradient(rgba(247,243,234,.018) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(247,243,234,.018) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:auto,auto,88px 88px,88px 88px;pointer-events:none;z-index:-1}
    a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
    .frame{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(248px,17vw) 1fr;min-height:100vh}
    .side{position:sticky;top:0;height:100vh;padding:20px 20px 18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;border-right:1px solid var(--line);overflow:hidden}
    .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
    .brand img{width:68px;height:68px;border-radius:20px;background:#fff}
    .brand strong{display:block;font:700 20px/1 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.055em}
    .brand span{display:block;color:var(--soft);font-size:17px}
    .intro-card{border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:20px 0;margin-top:30px}
    .intro-card p{font:600 17px/1.08 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.045em;color:#ebe5d8;margin:0}
    .side-viz{height:182px;margin-top:20px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:radial-gradient(circle at 42% 45%,rgba(215,255,111,.12),transparent 35%),radial-gradient(circle at 68% 70%,rgba(152,193,255,.10),transparent 36%),rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
    .side-viz canvas{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%}
    .side-viz:after{content:'dashboard case';position:absolute;left:16px;bottom:13px;color:var(--muted);font:700 9px 'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em}
    .side-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:8px;margin-top:14px}
    .stat,.hero-note,.controls-shell,.tab-copy,.kpi-shell,.kpi-card,.analytics-shell,.panel-card,.summary-card,.build-card,.repo-card,.readout-card,.narrative-card,.takeaway-shell{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:22px;background:var(--panel)}
    .stat{padding:12px 10px}
    .stat strong{display:block;font:700 20px/1 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.06em}
    .stat span,.eyebrow,.mini,.kpi-label,.panel-note,.summary-card span,.build-card span,.readout-label,.hero-metric-label{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em}
    .links{display:grid;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
    .links a{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:13px 4px;color:var(--soft);font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
    .main{padding:18px 26px 88px;min-width:0}
    .content{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto}
    .topnav{height:58px;display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;gap:20px;align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:sticky;top:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(5,5,5,.96),rgba(5,5,5,.72));backdrop-filter:blur(18px);z-index:20}
    .topnav a,.eyebrow,.reset-btn,summary,.filter-option label,.tab-button{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
    .topnav a{font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--soft);font-weight:800;white-space:nowrap}
    .lang{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:8px 10px;border-radius:999px}
    .dashboard-shell{padding-top:18px;display:grid;gap:0}
    .dashboard-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.06fr) minmax(320px,.94fr);gap:20px;align-items:stretch;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:0;border-radius:34px 34px 0 0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.06),rgba(255,255,255,.02))}
    .dashboard-head h1{font:700 clamp(42px,4.8vw,72px)/.88 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.085em;margin:8px 0 12px;max-width:10ch}
    .dashboard-head p{margin:0;color:#ddd6c7;font-size:16px;line-height:1.55;max-width:52ch}
    .mini-badges{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:14px}
    .badge{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 10px;color:var(--soft);font:700 10px 'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)}
    .hero-note{padding:22px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.06),rgba(255,255,255,.025));display:grid;gap:18px;align-content:space-between;border-radius:24px}
    .hero-note h2{margin:8px 0 0;font:700 22px/1.04 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.05em;max-width:16ch}
    .hero-note p{margin:0;color:var(--soft);font-size:14px;line-height:1.48}
    .hero-metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px}
    .hero-metric{padding:14px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.16)}
    .hero-metric strong{display:block;font-size:26px;letter-spacing:-.06em;color:#fffdf8}
    .stage-shell{padding:18px 0 0;display:grid;gap:18px}
    .controls-shell{padding:20px 24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),rgba(255,255,255,.02));display:grid;gap:14px;overflow:visible}
    .filter-toolbar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;align-items:center}
    .filter-toolbar h3{margin:0;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;color:var(--soft)}
    .filter-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;align-items:start;overflow:visible}
    details.filter-group{position:relative}
    details.filter-group summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--ink);font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;font-weight:700;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:15px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.045),rgba(255,255,255,.018))}
    details.filter-group summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
    .filter-options{display:none;gap:8px;max-height:220px;overflow:auto;padding-top:12px}
    details.filter-group[open]{z-index:15}
    details.filter-group[open] .filter-options{display:grid;position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:calc(100% + 8px);padding:14px 12px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;background:#0b0b0b;box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.42)}
    .filter-option{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;color:#efe9dc;font-size:13px}
    .filter-option input{margin-top:2px;accent-color:var(--acid)}
    .reset-btn{appearance:none;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--bg);padding:12px 15px;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer}
    .tabs-shell{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;padding:2px 0 0}
    .tab-button{appearance:none;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);color:var(--soft);padding:10px 15px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:background .18s ease,color .18s ease,border-color .18s ease}
    .tab-button:hover{border-color:rgba(247,243,234,.24);color:#f2ebdd}
    .tab-button.active{background:var(--acid);color:var(--bg);border-color:var(--acid)}
    .tab-copy{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px;align-items:start;padding:20px 24px 22px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.045),rgba(255,255,255,.02))}
    .tab-copy h3{margin:0;font:700 34px/.95 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.06em;max-width:16ch}
    .tab-copy p{margin:6px 0 0;color:var(--soft);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;max-width:58ch}
    .tab-rail{display:none}
    .kpi-shell{padding:18px 20px 20px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.032),rgba(255,255,255,.014));border-radius:30px}
    .kpi-band{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px;padding:0}
    .kpi-card{padding:16px 14px 14px;min-height:96px;display:grid;align-content:end;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.085),rgba(255,255,255,.035));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:18px}
    .kpi-value{font:700 30px/.92 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.07em;color:#fffdf8}
    .analytics-shell{padding:28px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),rgba(255,255,255,.018));display:grid;gap:28px;border-radius:34px}
    .dashboard-sectors{display:grid;gap:30px;padding:0}
    .sector-block{display:grid;grid-template-columns:260px 1fr;gap:28px;padding:28px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:34px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04),rgba(255,255,255,.012))}
    .sector-head{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px;align-items:start;padding:6px 22px 6px 2px;border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .sector-head h4{margin:0;font:700 24px/.98 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.05em}
    .sector-head p{margin:0;color:var(--soft);font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;max-width:32ch}
    .sector-panels{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:26px;align-items:stretch}
    .panel-card{padding:0;min-height:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(17,17,17,.96),rgba(10,10,10,.92));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);display:grid;grid-template-rows:auto 1fr;align-content:start;overflow:hidden;border-radius:28px;box-shadow:0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.24),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
    .panel-head{display:grid;gap:7px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:0;padding:20px 22px 16px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),rgba(255,255,255,.012));border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10)}
    .panel-head h3{margin:0;font:700 19px/1.06 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.045em;max-width:15ch}
    .panel-note{font-size:9px;color:#bdb7a8}
    .chart-shell{align-self:end;margin:16px;padding:18px 18px 16px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);border-radius:22px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.02),rgba(0,0,0,.18));box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
    .chart-shell svg{display:block;width:100%;height:auto}
    .list-shell{display:grid;gap:10px}
    .list-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) auto;gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:12px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .list-row:first-child{border-top:0;padding-top:0}
    .list-row strong{display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:1.3}
    .list-row span{display:block;color:var(--soft);font-size:12px;line-height:1.35}
    .list-row em{font-style:normal;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;color:#fffaf2}
    .analytics-foot{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.05fr) minmax(340px,.95fr);gap:18px;align-items:start}
    .takeaway-shell{padding:22px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),rgba(255,255,255,.022));border-radius:26px}
    .readout-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:16px;padding:14px 0 0}
    .readout-card{padding:18px 18px 20px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.035);min-height:118px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:20px}
    .readout-card strong{display:block;font:700 22px/1 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.05em;color:#fffdf8}
    .readout-card span{display:block;margin-top:5px;color:var(--soft);font-size:12px;line-height:1.35}
    .narrative-card{padding:24px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.05),rgba(255,255,255,.02))}
    .narrative-card-wide{margin:0}
    .narrative-card h3{margin:10px 0 14px;font:700 24px/1 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.04em}
    .narrative-copy{display:grid;gap:12px}
    .narrative-copy article{padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
    .narrative-copy article:first-child{padding-top:0;border-top:0}
    .narrative-copy h4{margin:0 0 6px;font:700 18px/1.08 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.03em}
    .narrative-copy p{margin:0;color:var(--soft);font-size:14px;line-height:1.45}
    .below-fold{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:24px;margin-top:32px;align-items:start}
    .summary-card,.repo-card{padding:28px}
    .summary-card h2,.repo-card h2{font:700 30px/.96 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.07em;margin:10px 0 14px;max-width:15ch}
    .summary-list{display:grid;gap:14px}
    .summary-list article{padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
    .summary-list article:first-child{padding-top:0;border-top:0}
    .summary-list h3{margin:0 0 8px;font:700 18px/1.06 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.04em}
    .summary-list p,.repo-card p,.build-card p{margin:0;color:var(--soft);line-height:1.5}
    .repo-actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:18px}
    .repo-actions a{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;padding:12px 15px;font-weight:800}
    .repo-actions a.primary{background:var(--acid);border-color:var(--acid);color:#030303}
    .build-shell{margin-top:18px;padding:22px 24px 24px !important;border-radius:30px !important;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04),rgba(255,255,255,.02)) !important}
    .build-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:12px;margin-top:14px}
    .build-card{padding:18px}
    .build-card h3{margin:12px 0 8px;font:700 19px/1.06 var(--heading);letter-spacing:-.04em}
    .empty-state{padding:18px;border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:18px;color:var(--soft);font-size:14px}
    @media(max-width:1280px){
      .dashboard-head,.tab-copy,.below-fold,.build-grid,.analytics-foot{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .kpi-band{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr))}
      .sector-block{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .sector-head{padding:0 0 16px;border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
      .readout-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}
    }
    @media(max-width:980px){
      .frame{display:block}
      .side{position:relative;height:auto;border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:18px}
      .main{padding:0 18px 70px}
      .content{max-width:none}
      .topnav{justify-content:flex-start;overflow-x:auto;gap:10px;height:auto;padding:12px 0}
      .topnav a{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.06em;flex:0 0 auto;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 10px}
      .dashboard-shell{padding-top:18px}
      .filter-row,.sector-panels,.build-grid,.below-fold{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .kpi-band{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}
      .controls-shell,.tab-copy,.takeaway-shell,.narrative-card-wide,.build-shell{padding-left:18px;padding-right:18px}
    }
    @media(max-width:560px){
      .main{padding-left:14px;padding-right:14px}
      .side{padding:16px}
      .kpi-band,.readout-grid,.hero-metrics,.build-grid,.below-fold{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .dashboard-head h1{font-size:38px}
      .dashboard-head p{font-size:14px}
      .filter-toolbar{display:grid}
      .reset-btn{width:100%}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="frame">
    <aside class="side">
      <div>
        <a class="brand" href="/pt/">
          <img src="/assets/logo/monogram.svg" alt="" />
          <div>
            <strong>Luanda Rodrigues,</strong>
            <span>Analista de Dados</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <div class="intro-card">
          <p>Um case com foco em BI mostrando como sinais de workforce podem virar um produto analítico mais limpo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="side-viz" aria-label="Visual abstrato de dados">
          <canvas id="sideGraphCanvas"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="side-stats">
          <div class="stat"><strong>02</strong><span>segundo destaque</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>BI</strong><span>foco em painel</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>PT/EN</strong><span>case page</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="/pt/">Portfólio <span>Abrir</span></a>
        <a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues/workforce-labor-market-intelligence-bi-suite">Repositório <span>Abrir</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luanda-rodrigues">LinkedIn <span>Abrir</span></a>
        <a href="/workforce-intelligence">English <span>Ver</span></a>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <main class="main">
      <div class="content">
        <nav class="topnav">
          <a href="#dashboard">Painel</a>
          <a href="#summary">Resumo</a>
          <a href="#build">Construção</a>
          <a href="#repo">Repo</a>
          <a class="lang" href="/workforce-intelligence">EN</a>
        </nav>

        <section class="dashboard-shell" id="dashboard">
          <div class="dashboard-head">
            <div>
              <span class="eyebrow">People Analytics / Produto de BI / Workforce Planning</span>
              <h1>Workforce & Labor Market Intelligence</h1>
              <p>
                Um painel de workforce mais limpo, combinando sinais internos de RH, pressão de mercado
                e risco de turnover em uma camada reutilizável de BI.
              </p>
              <div class="mini-badges">
                <span class="badge">Python</span>
                <span class="badge">SQL</span>
                <span class="badge">DuckDB</span>
                <span class="badge">Risco de attrition</span>
                <span class="badge">Outputs prontos para BI</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-note">
              <div>
                <span class="mini">Pergunta central</span>
                <h2>Onde a prioridade de retenção deve entrar primeiro quando risco interno e pressão externa andam juntos?</h2>
              </div>
              <p>Use os filtros, troque a visão analítica e leia o painel como um produto de decisão, não como uma página estática.</p>
              <div class="hero-metrics" id="heroHighlights"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stage-shell">
          <div class="controls-shell">
            <div class="filter-toolbar">
              <h3>Filtrar o recorte atual</h3>
              <button class="reset-btn" id="resetFilters" type="button">Limpar filtros</button>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-row" id="filterBar"></div>
            <div class="tabs-shell" id="tabBar"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-copy">
            <div>
              <span class="eyebrow" id="tabEyebrow">Visão executiva</span>
              <h3 id="tabTitle">Leitura executiva da força de trabalho</h3>
              <p id="tabText">Este recorte junta tamanho da força de trabalho, attrition, prioridade de retenção e pressão de mercado em uma leitura única.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-rail" id="tabRail"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="kpi-shell">
            <div class="kpi-band" id="kpiBand"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="analytics-shell">
          <div class="dashboard-sectors" id="dashboardGrid"></div>
          <div class="analytics-foot">
          <div class="takeaway-shell">
            <span class="eyebrow">Leituras do recorte atual</span>
            <div class="readout-grid" id="readoutGrid"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="narrative-card narrative-card-wide">
            <span class="readout-label">Notas de decisão</span>
            <h3 id="narrativeTitle">O que mais chama atenção no recorte atual</h3>
            <div class="narrative-copy" id="insightCopy"></div>
          </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="below-fold" id="summary">
          <div class="summary-card">
            <span class="eyebrow">Resumo executivo</span>
            <h2>O que este painel está mostrando.</h2>
            <div class="summary-list">
              <article>
                <h3>Attrition faz mais sentido com contexto</h3>
                <p>O objetivo aqui não é só mostrar quem pode sair, mas combinar risco interno, exposição de custo e pressão de mercado na mesma leitura.</p>
              </article>
              <article>
                <h3>Prioridade importa mais que turnover bruto</h3>
                <p>Os departamentos mais urgentes nem sempre são os que têm attrition mais alto isoladamente. A leitura de prioridade é o que torna essa camada mais operacional.</p>
              </article>
              <article>
                <h3>O output foi feito para ser reaproveitado</h3>
